===Etymology===
From Scandinavian. Swedish ''[[köping]]'' is from the same source and the root appears in Finnish ''[[kauppa]]'' "shop", Swedish ''[[köpa]]'' "to buy", German ''[[kaufen]]'' "to buy" and English ''[[cheap]]''. Originally from Latin, cf. [[caupo]].

